## component registry export
command=nix develop --no-update-lock-file . -c bash -lc mkdir\ -p\ target/component-registry\ \&\&\ nickel\ export\ compat/config/component-registry.ncl\ \>\ target/component-registry/component-registry.json 
mc compat shell: use 'mc-compat-runner --dry-run' or 'nix run .#mc-compat-smoke -- --run'
Stevenarella dev env: cargo/rustc/xvfb-run/OpenSSL/fontconfig/freetype/libxcb paths are available
OnixResearch tools are pinned over SSH: cairn, cargo-octet
Steel is available for repo scripts, e.g. steel scripts/ralph-drain-cairns.scm --self-test
exit_status=0

